<body>
	<div class="content">
		<h1 class="header1">Table Of Content</h1>
		<ol>
			<li>Introduction</li>
		 <li>Summary of Procuring Agency's Task </li>
		 <li>Accessing CiNet</li>
		 <li>Dashboard</li>
		 <li>Upload Tender</li>
		 <li>List of Uploaded Tender</li>
		 <li>Bidding Form.....</li>
		 <li>Edit Bidding Form</li>
